# Overall TODO

Features:
    - Add support for custom partition layouts.
      - /boot presence/absence and fs type, keeping /efi separate.
      - /boot being just the EPS (vfat), thus merged /efi and /boot into one (/efi/boot or /efi/grub).
      - vector upgrade should be updated too.
    - Create matrixos-uki ebuild (like -initramfs, but that builds a UKI), add imager tests for such deployment.
    - [sd-boot] Closely watch https://github.com/ostreedev/ostree/pull/3359 (PR still open, but we have the patches)
        This will be our trampoline to support bootc in the future.
        Step 1: support sd-boot alongside grub2, start building new images with sd-boot.
        Step 2: switch to UKI.
        Step 3: add bootc support.
    - Add UKI building to kernel build (make USE flag optional).
    - Investigate root-less builds using unshare.
    - Support Cloud Init (add VM tests).
